title: This academic year, 19,904 students were enrolled at Radboud University (Radboud Universiteit)
text: ( Source : Radboud Universiteit) 19,904 students are being educated at Radboud University during the 2015-2016 academic year. This is an increase of 219 students and has resulted in a new record being set. Master's studies at Radboud
